The paper deals with privacy-preserving data aggregation, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR). It also involves optimization and statistical analysis (cs.LG, cs.IT), as well as data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the incorporation of prior knowledge and context-awareness, which are topics in social and information sciences (cs.SI).
